About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • 40W Dual PD Port Fast Charging: UGREEN PD car charger saves time for driver and passenger by simultaneously charging USB-C smartphones and tablets at full speed. With the max power of 40W, the powerful power delivery3.0 technology guarantees super-fast charging of your USB-C devices.
  • Premium materials and design: UGREEN Type C car charger is made of alloy with a scratch-resistant surface suitable for the most untouched vehicle interiors. Gold-plated tubing reduces heat during charging while maximizing charging speed and efficiency. The mini thumb-sized design saves space and enables seamless access to the rest of the dashboard.
  • Intelligent protection: UGREEN dual-port car adatper has an integrated intelligent power management chip that automatically offers over-temperature, over-current, over-charging, over-voltage protection, therefore it provides stable performance through a series of charging tests and quality assurance.
  • Universal compatibility: With the application of 12V-24V voltage, UGREEN USB-C PD3.0 car charger works flawlessly with all kinds of cars/trucks/vans, and rapid charge for iPhone 12/12 Mini/12Pro Max/11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/SE/8/7, Samsung GalaxyS21/S20/S20+/S10+/S10e/Note 20/Note 10, Google Pixel 5/5a/4 XL/4/3 XL/3/3a/3a XL, LG G8 ThinQ/V50, Moto G7 and more.
  • Fearless bumps: The shrapnel contact design enables the car charger to be plugged in firmly no matter how bumpy the road is. UGREEN car phone charger can provide a stable power supply for the device. It is suitable for you to bring it to travel facing all kinds of road conditions.

      40W Dual PD Port Fast Charging: UGREEN PD car charger can simultaneously charge two devices such as mobile phone and tablet. The powerful power delivery technology guarantees super-fast charging of your USB-C devices. With the max power of 40W, the powerful car charger saves time for driver and passenger by simultaneously charging USB-C smartphones and tablets at full speed via Type-C Power Delivery 3.0.

      UGREEN 40W Universal Dual PD Fast-Charging Car Charger

      Q: Will this USB C car charger FAST CHARGE my phone?

      A: Yes. This USB car charger features with 2 USB-C PD 3.0 ports, which makes it can fast charge all prevailing phones.

      Compatible with iPhone 8/8P/X/XS/XS Max/11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/SE/12/12Mini/12Pro Max

      Compatible with Google Pixel 2/3/3A/4/XL/5/5a

      Compatible with Samsung Galaxy S8/9/10/Plus NOTE 9/10+/S20/S20/S20+/S21/S21+

      Compatible with iPad Air/Pro/Mini, Motorola, LG, Sony, Nexus, HTC, etc.

      Q: Is this fast car charger made of metal?

      A: Yes. We carefully select metal as shell brass material, so that our customers needn't worry about plastic-melting or over-heating problem.

      Q: Is this dual USB car charger smaller than other PD car charger?

      A: Yes. We get away from the big-head design of traditional PD car chargers so that UGREEN fast car chargers can be smaller than those in the market and save more space.

      Q:Can this car charger support charging two mobile phones?

      AYES!! It can charge 2 devices at the same time at full speed with twin USB-C charging ports.

      Extensive Compatibility

      High-powered USB outputs are universally compatible with almost USB C mobile devices.

      Fearless bumps

      Stable charging without fear of bumps.

      Uncompromising Safety Standards

      Our unique Safety System protects against shorts, surges, and other dangers to keep you and your devices safe.
